Info:
The map is called aim_"OCTA"_v1, because of the small building in the middle of the map. The building has eight sides to
it and this is whee i got the name from.

The map is for 20 players (10 terroists and 10 counter-terrorists)

The weapons avaiable are knife, USP, glock, deagles, m4a1 and AK47's, which you will see everywhere throughout the map.

THERE ARE 2 HIDDEN M3'S HIDDEN SOMEWHERE IN THE MAP!! SEE IF YOU CAN FIND THEM AND GIVE ME A POST IF YOU DO. 

There not that hard to find but I just thought I'd do it anywayz!! 

Other Stuff to know about:

DONT EDIT THE MAP WITHOUT MY PERMISSION!!!!

AS LONG AS YOU TELL ME FIRST AND TELL ME WHAT YOUR DOING TO THE MAP, I WILL LET YOU EDIT IT.

If anyone wants any maps making, post me your idea and i'll see whati can do. 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Thank You and Enjoy aim_octa_v1!!
